1. *Častim* te pićem. (I'm treating you to a drink.)
2. Ja *častim* večeru. (I'm treating dinner.)
3. *Častiš* li nekog? (Are you treating someone?)
4. *Časti* nas sutra za rođendan. (Treat us tomorrow for a birthday.)
5. *Častio bih* tebe ali mi je novčanik ostao kod kuće. (I would treat you, but I left my wallet at home.)
6. On *časti* svog oca kad god mu treba pomoć. (He treats his father whenever he needs help.)
7. Žena me *častila* kolačem. (The woman treated me with cake.)
8. *Častite li* vaše goste dobrodošlicom? (Do you treat your guests with a warm welcome?)
9. *Častili su* nas besplatnom ulaznicom. (They treated us with a free ticket.)
10. *Častio sam* kolege u kancelariji sa slatkišima. (I treated my colleagues in the office with sweets.)

Note: In all these examples, the word "častim" and its different forms have the meaning of treating someone or something.